Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕  你流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要趕快做點處理才行
